OL,3,CUK's civil service chief Simon Case
OL,4,Cset to resign on health grounds
OL,6,FThe UK's top civil servant Simon Case
OL,7,Fhas announced he will resign at the
OL,8,Fend of the year on health grounds.
OL,10,FCabinet Secretary Mr Case, who has
OL,11,Fbeen undergoing treatment for a
OL,12,Fneurological condition, told
OL,13,Fcolleagues "whilst the spirit remains
OL,14,Fwilling, the body is not".
OL,16,FThere have been reports of tensions at
OL,17,Fthe heart of No 10 between Mr Case and
OL,18,FSir Keir Starmer's chief of staff Sue
OL,19,FGray.
