OL,6,FHowever, the Cabinet Secretary said:
OL,7,F"It is a shame that I feel I have to
OL,8,Fspell this out, but my decision is
OL,9,Fsolely to do with my health and
OL,10,Fnothing to do with anything else."
OL,12,FThe 45-year-old returned to work in
OL,13,FJanuary after two months off sick and
OL,14,Fsaid he had been "undergoing medical
OL,15,Ftreatment for a neurological condition
OL,16,Fover the last 18 months".
OL,18,FA recruitment process for the next
OL,19,Fcabinet secretary has begun.
