OL,6,FIn a nod to the the turbulence in
OL,7,FBritish politics, Mr Case said: "It
OL,8,Fhas been an honour to serve two
OL,9,Fsovereigns, four prime ministers, and
OL,10,Fover 120 cabinet ministers in this
OL,11,Frole.
OL,13,F"There have been far more ups than
OL,14,Fdowns along the way and by far the
OL,15,Fgreatest highlight has been the
OL,16,Fprivilege of working with so many
OL,17,Fremarkable public servants, across the
OL,18,Flength and breadth of our country, in
OL,19,Four overseas posts and with
OL,20,Fcounterparts from our close allies and
OL,21,Fpartners around the world."
