OL,6,FHe was appointed as cabinet secretary
OL,7,Fby former Prime Minister Boris Johnson
OL,8,Fin September 2020.
OL,10,FEvidence at the UK Covid-19 Inquiry
OL,11,Frevealed the administration often
OL,12,Firritated him.
OL,14,FHe described Mr Johnson's work style
OL,15,Fas "very frustrating" and said his day-
OL,16,Fto-day administration was
OL,17,F"dysfunctional".
